metadata.name: X&ND Livestream: Rise of X&ND Miami
metadata.description:
This historic livestream marks X&ND's first combined performance; performing live for XANDYLANDERS and Superpass holders in Miami while live streaming globally. After a series of powerful live performances throughout Art Basel Miami, X&ND is wrapping up the week with an intimate performance for the community whilst opening the gates to join the Rise of X&ND community.
